  <entry>
    <id>https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/releases/tag/v3.0.0</id>
    <title>New release for Zitadel: v3.0.0</title>
    <updated>2025-05-02T08:22:38-04:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>zitadel/zitadel</name>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;h1&gt;&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/compare/v2.71.8...v3.0.0"&gt;3.0.0&lt;/a&gt; (2025-05-02)&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Highlights&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;License Change&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Zitadel Repository changes from an Apache 2.0 to an AGPL3 License&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Cockroach DB Support Removed&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Breaking&lt;/strong&gt;: Cockroach DB support is removed (https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/pull/9444)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Please check out the documentation to migrate from cockroach to postgres: https://zitadel.com/docs/self-hosting/manage/cli/mirror &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Actions V2&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Action V2 management is available in Zitadel management console (https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/pull/9591)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Breaking&lt;/strong&gt;: The action management API is now available as beta in the API V2 (previously existing requests in API v3 alpha are removed) (https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/pull/9489)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Web Keys Management&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;OIDC Web key management is available in Zitadel management console (https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/pull/9526)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Breaking&lt;/strong&gt;: The web key management API is now available as beta in the API V2 (previously existing requests in API v3 alpha are removed) (https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/pull/9445)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Others&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Newly implemented permission check framework supports system user (https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/pull/9640)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Zitadel management console supports Zitadel V2 API (available through a feature flag)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;user creation (https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/pull/9506)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;list sessions (https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/pull/9539)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Zitadel management console supports all currently available feature flags (https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/pull/9682)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Full Changelog&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Bug Fixes&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Actions V2 improve deleted target handling in executions (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/issues/9822"&gt;#9822&lt;/a&gt;) (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/commit/8bd7414241773c0bc3d603495efd87b529ed754d"&gt;8bd7414&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;actions:&lt;/strong&gt; correctly handle api.v1.appendUserGrant (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/issues/9598"&gt;#9598&lt;/a&gt;) (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/commit/57bfecf7f77bf33881a0368d25b7c1004f03d535"&gt;57bfecf&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;actions:&lt;/strong&gt; default sorting column to creation date (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/issues/9795"&gt;#9795&lt;/a&gt;) (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/commit/24cbeb64c8230729119f89ac93f89b02f2527d2b"&gt;24cbeb6&lt;/a&gt;), closes &lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/issues/9763"&gt;#9763&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;actions:&lt;/strong&gt; handle empty deny list correctly (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/issues/9753"&gt;#9753&lt;/a&gt;) (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/commit/cd19b264b3720c38f4d160585dbfd2017582bc46"&gt;cd19b26&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;actions:&lt;/strong&gt; Linking external account doesn't trigger flow "External Authentication" on "Post Authentication" on first login (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/issues/9397"&gt;#9397&lt;/a&gt;) (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/commit/b0fa974419867a56d3a40dfee715460fd785a119"&gt;b0fa974&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;add permission check for saml request query (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/issues/9520"&gt;#9520&lt;/a&gt;) (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/commit/5eb3a543e818c42edda30aec07e80e330db229af"&gt;5eb3a54&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;allow native applications to use https:// on loopback redirect addresses (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/issues/9073"&gt;#9073&lt;/a&gt;) (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/commit/8b1b9cbb982d46d5571e4aa2db7bbed29bb83183"&gt;8b1b9cb&lt;/a&gt;), closes &lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/issues/4091"&gt;#4091&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Auto cleanup failed Setup steps if process is killed (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/issues/9736"&gt;#9736&lt;/a&gt;) (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/commit/7fceb5eaf87b670a1de89764f18dca54346338b4"&gt;7fceb5e&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;cmd:&lt;/strong&gt; clarify notification config handling (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/issues/9459"&gt;#9459&lt;/a&gt;) (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/commit/92f0cf018f355693f763b265efb74c64f63beed5"&gt;92f0cf0&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;console:&lt;/strong&gt; allow management of metadata of users of other organizations again (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/issues/9490"&gt;#9490&lt;/a&gt;) (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/commit/61c4b1c3fd3a4260d91d8626a604d2d4177edb34"&gt;61c4b1c&lt;/a&gt;), closes &lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/issues/9488"&gt;#9488&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;console:&lt;/strong&gt; correct count for users list, show create timestamp in user details (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/issues/9705"&gt;#9705&lt;/a&gt;) (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/commit/051c36588bc49db77ad3effb1696f3bca2252da6"&gt;051c365&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;console:&lt;/strong&gt; Implement generic feature toggle (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/issues/9516"&gt;#9516&lt;/a&gt;) (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/commit/83108d1dc3ab76bae0ff2ed892524a571bea6fbf"&gt;83108d1&lt;/a&gt;), closes &lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/issues/9090"&gt;#9090&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;console:&lt;/strong&gt; list of unique v2 sessions (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/issues/9778"&gt;#9778&lt;/a&gt;) (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/commit/ba3cfd7baec24e78ee5ec2b83b43ff8a7637fe15"&gt;ba3cfd7&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;console:&lt;/strong&gt; pass verification code for phone verification (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/issues/9616"&gt;#9616&lt;/a&gt;) (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/commit/54e513f312eb6364b1db4d79063bfe08e7bea279"&gt;54e513f&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;correct event type for permission removed (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/issues/9626"&gt;#9626&lt;/a&gt;) (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/commit/e7c7f9b800dcb01bf4307bde9d7f957dfad62a02"&gt;e7c7f9b&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;correct handling of removed targets (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/issues/9824"&gt;#9824&lt;/a&gt;) (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/commit/bd75b8c9bdd0a0fb0083a1602544f0e36fdccad1"&gt;bd75b8c&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;correct unmarshalling of IdP user when using Google (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/issues/9799"&gt;#9799&lt;/a&gt;) (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/commit/496d69487f0d11941b7b12db72bc046e195a7912"&gt;496d694&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;eventstore:&lt;/strong&gt; optimise query hints for event filters (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/issues/9497"&gt;#9497&lt;/a&gt;) (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/commit/b5781371395a1f4b7ad7ae8c5ff567193f71b4d2"&gt;b578137&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;features:&lt;/strong&gt; remove the improved performance enumer (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/issues/9819"&gt;#9819&lt;/a&gt;) (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/commit/98d5e97ad4fe9578508d446a73928e3f2ebb4a96"&gt;98d5e97&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Improve Actions V2 Texts and reenable in settings (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/issues/9814"&gt;#9814&lt;/a&gt;) (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/commit/0af5346288e6634d95da873e64cb2c84cf112885"&gt;0af5346&lt;/a&gt;), closes &lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/issues/7248"&gt;#7248&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/issues/9688"&gt;#9688&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Improve Actions V2 translations (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/issues/9826"&gt;#9826&lt;/a&gt;) (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/commit/cf3f02237db7090042013fdf0d74a008f2d006c0"&gt;cf3f022&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;instance:&lt;/strong&gt; add web key generation to instance defaults (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/issues/9815"&gt;#9815&lt;/a&gt;) (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/commit/19aacdab26373c3d331bd0c788cea61da1cbf23e"&gt;19aacda&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;login:&lt;/strong&gt; cache scripts and other assets correctly (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/issues/9551"&gt;#9551&lt;/a&gt;) (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/commit/19f022e1cf6c62c1cff03fc1e945c6b8a094c6c6"&gt;19f022e&lt;/a&gt;), closes &lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/issues/9485"&gt;#9485&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;login:&lt;/strong&gt; handle requests without auth request correctly (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/issues/9713"&gt;#9713&lt;/a&gt;) (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/commit/79a5585f91d104af3d25cfcb9a8d7d79067e15d7"&gt;79a5585&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;login:&lt;/strong&gt; improve webauthn error handling (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/issues/9474"&gt;#9474&lt;/a&gt;) (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/commit/a82f5805b6acf6e4b22bee927119c326e8bf5df6"&gt;a82f580&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;login:&lt;/strong&gt; passkey setup when pressing "Enter" key on login form (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/issues/9485"&gt;#9485&lt;/a&gt;) (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/commit/27b319bd988f49d2feb6352ea2f2ad21e68646b7"&gt;27b319b&lt;/a&gt;), closes &lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/issues/6592"&gt;#6592&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/issues/2910"&gt;#2910&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;migration:&lt;/strong&gt; check if ldap2 already exists (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/issues/9674"&gt;#9674&lt;/a&gt;) (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/commit/2eb187f1410a25e80ff86255923d534041c8d139"&gt;2eb187f&lt;/a&gt;), closes &lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/issues/9669"&gt;#9669&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;milestone multiple results per instance domain instead of primary instance domain (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/issues/9564"&gt;#9564&lt;/a&gt;) (&lt;a href="https://github.com/zitadel/zitadel/commit/352fa6aa6f478f6ba1da0033daf3a0e2c02b2719"&gt;352fa6a&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
